[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":187},["ShallowReactive",2],{"portfolio-vital-access":3},{"page":4,"next":165},{"id":5,"slug":6,"title":7,"displayTitle":8,"intro":9,"featuredMedia":10,"blocks":31},"D5CqpIg_RA-DNsC_w4P5Iw","vital-access","ASKLYZE","Where Oracle APEX analytics meets AI innovation.","\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>ASKLYZE\u003C/strong> transforms Oracle APEX applications into intelligent analytics experiences, helping teams explore data, generate insights, and build dashboards using natural language.\u003C/p>",{"id":11,"media":12,"device":30},"Rp5KiVCsTxyxuSHaLX8PBg",{"id":13,"alt":14,"title":14,"focalPoint":15,"width":17,"height":18,"thumbnail":19,"small":20,"medium":21,"responsiveImage":22,"video":14},"AVllGn5ESNey_EsZKs3b6Q",null,{"x":16,"y":16},0.5,1338,1003,"/home.mp4","/home.mp4","/home.mp4",{"srcSet":23,"webpSrcSet":24,"sizes":25,"src":26,"width":17,"height":18,"aspectRatio":27,"alt":14,"title":14,"base64":28,"bgColor":29},"/home.mp4","","(max-width: 1338px) 100vw, 1338px","/home.mp4",1.3339980059820538,"data:image/png;base64,","#26507d","tablet",[32,100,153],{"id":33,"type":34,"device":30,"items":35},"XZ9wI1lHSNmIB_9v1Gy89A","steps_block",[36,60,83],{"id":37,"media":38,"title":41,"subtitle":42,"text":43,"list":44,"link":56},"Its6VKIqRAiqgKGFqJzfnw",{"id":13,"alt":14,"title":14,"focalPoint":39,"width":17,"height":18,"thumbnail":19,"small":20,"medium":21,"responsiveImage":40,"video":14},{"x":16,"y":16},{"srcSet":23,"webpSrcSet":24,"sizes":25,"src":26,"width":17,"height":18,"aspectRatio":27,"alt":14,"title":14,"base64":28,"bgColor":29},"Product Snapshot.","What we built and why we built it.","\u003Cp>\u003Cspan data-metadata=\"&lt;!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiWUpTZ21aZGdNTDlvRWR2YmZ1cjZJdCIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjIwMzUyMTEyOTMsImRhdGFUeXBlIjoic2NlbmUifQo=(/figmeta)--&gt;\">\u003C/span>ASKLYZE is a customer-facing dashboard designed to bring clarity to some of the most complex parts of market access. Built in close partnership with Profero&mdash;leaders in access strategy&mdash;it brings together real-time data on coverage, affordability, and reimbursement in a way that feels familiar, fast, and actually helpful to the people using it.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Designed for iPads, deployed inside Veeva, and shaped with reps in mind from day one, this tool doesn&rsquo;t just fit into the workflow&mdash;it improves it. It&rsquo;s smart, simple, and built with care. Because that&rsquo;s how we work. And because the right tools, built the right way, can change how a conversation starts&mdash;and where it goes.\u003C/p>",[45,48,52],{"id":46,"label":47,"text":7},"BdmUSeStTOGJAD0qOyImEQ","Product Name",{"id":49,"label":50,"text":51},"DlqS_bp-RKCmh_q9qmGe3w","Launched","June 2025",{"id":53,"label":54,"text":55},"Fo5RlIOFTDyUVfGsxM2Cjg","Type","Internal Sales Tool / iPad (Veeva)",{"id":57,"label":58,"internal":14,"external":59},"dw3p4Jl5TuCqhvQ3zNfU4g","Contact Us to Schedule a Demo","mailto:info@builtkindly.com?subject=Schedule a Time Being Demo",{"id":61,"media":62,"title":79,"subtitle":80,"text":81,"list":82,"link":14},"J2mtRwrVRiyuMpgsDIyZFQ",{"id":63,"alt":14,"title":14,"focalPoint":64,"width":65,"height":66,"thumbnail":67,"small":68,"medium":69,"responsiveImage":70,"video":14},"RDCuFU5XTO2DwnFOjhh9og",{"x":16,"y":16},2732,2048,"https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1756769071-va_dp.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=600&q=85&w=600","https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1756769071-va_dp.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=1000&q=85&w=1000","https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1756769071-va_dp.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=1500&q=85&w=1500",{"srcSet":71,"webpSrcSet":24,"sizes":72,"src":73,"width":74,"height":75,"aspectRatio":76,"alt":14,"title":14,"base64":77,"bgColor":78},"https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1756769071-va_dp.png?auto=format&dpr=0.25&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 610w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1756769071-va_dp.png?auto=format&dpr=0.5&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 1220w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1756769071-va_dp.png?auto=format&dpr=0.75&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 1830w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1756769071-va_dp.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 2440w","(max-width: 2440px) 100vw, 2440px","https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1756769071-va_dp.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440",2440,1829,1.333984375,"data:image/jpeg;base64,","#3787b4","The Spark.","We knew field teams could do more. With the right tool.","\u003Cp>The access story is never one-size-fits-all. Reps need to pivot in real time, shift the conversation, and speak to what matters&mdash;coverage, affordability, and reimbursement. But the tools they had weren&rsquo;t built for that. So we built one that was.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>ASKLYZE puts real data in the rep&rsquo;s hands, right when they need it, wrapped in an interface that&rsquo;s simple, smart, and actually shaped around how they work. No noise. No friction. Just a clearer way to meet every conversation where it is.\u003C/p>",[],{"id":84,"media":85,"title":96,"subtitle":97,"text":98,"list":99,"link":14},"ENlRws70Qp2rWjICoqdGug",{"id":86,"alt":14,"title":14,"focalPoint":87,"width":65,"height":66,"thumbnail":88,"small":89,"medium":90,"responsiveImage":91,"video":14},"RVzwz9RfSe63wH-Lu_u0vw",{"x":16,"y":16},"https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1756769606-va_home.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=600&q=85&w=600","https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1756769606-va_home.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=1000&q=85&w=1000","https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1756769606-va_home.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=1500&q=85&w=1500",{"srcSet":92,"webpSrcSet":24,"sizes":72,"src":93,"width":74,"height":75,"aspectRatio":76,"alt":14,"title":14,"base64":94,"bgColor":95},"https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1756769606-va_home.png?auto=format&dpr=0.25&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 610w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1756769606-va_home.png?auto=format&dpr=0.5&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 1220w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1756769606-va_home.png?auto=format&dpr=0.75&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 1830w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1756769606-va_home.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 2440w","https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1756769606-va_home.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440","data:image/jpeg;base64,","#d88d3a","The Problem.","The problem we couldn't ignore","\u003Cp data-start=\"144\" data-end=\"403\">Access teams had the data, but getting to it meant jumping between PDFs, clunky portals, and tools that didn&rsquo;t speak the same language. Insights weren&rsquo;t missing. They were just buried.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp data-start=\"405\" data-end=\"544\">Everything felt disconnected: the workflow, the design, the story. And none of it looked or felt like the brand it was supposed to support.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp data-start=\"546\" data-end=\"671\">So we built something better. A tool that fits the workflow. Honors the brand. And makes access data feel like second nature.\u003C/p>",[],{"id":101,"type":102,"title":103,"subtitle":104,"text1":105,"text2":106,"media":107},"WjTYEdAhSn2e21M-AmL0Ig","image_grid_block","The Process","From idea to “oh yeah, this is slick”.","\u003Cp>Profero knew exactly what the field needed, because they&rsquo;ve been here before. With years of experience navigating market access and building similar tools, they came to the table with real clarity: the data and customizability that was needed, the patterns they&rsquo;d seen succeed, and the gaps that kept showing up. And what was missing: a better experience to deliver it.\u003C/p>","\u003Cp>That&rsquo;s where we came in. APEX Experts partnered with our Veeva-savvy friends at Envivent to help bring Profero&rsquo;s ideas and data to life, turning them into something real, deceptively simple, and genuinely powerful, with intuitive editing, built-in email functionality, and smart, search-driven navigation.\u003C/p>",[108,123,138],{"id":109,"alt":14,"title":14,"focalPoint":110,"width":111,"height":112,"thumbnail":113,"small":114,"medium":115,"responsi